articles.description: Yante Maten scored 23 points, including a huge 3-pointer to send the game into overtime, and Georgia beat Florida 72-69 Wednesday night to end a three-game losing streak in Southeastern Conference play.
articles.headline: Maten scores 23, Georgia sweeps Florida with 72-69 OT win

articles.description: Trevon Bluiett puts up a game-high 37 points and grabs seven boards as No. 4 Xavier tops Seton Hall 102-90.
articles.headline: Bluiett leads Xavier past Seton Hall

articles.description: No. 10 Auburn outlasts Kentucky at home behind 18 points each from Bryce Brown and Jared Harper.
articles.headline: Auburn sends Kentucky to 4th straight loss with 76-66 win

articles.headline: New Mexico beats Utah State 78-63
